column2: Press Esc to cancel this operation
column3: Presiona Esc para cancelar esta operación
column5: 按 Esc 键取消更新
column6: 按 Esc 鍵取消更新

column7: 名前を入れてください。
ポート番号を入れてください。
ロビー名を入れてください。
パスワードを入れてください。
ファイルセレクトへ戻る
モードセレクトへ戻る

column2: Play on a board, collect the most Shines and become the party star!
column3: ¡Juega en un tablero y consigue muchos Soles para ser la estrella de la fiesta!
column4: 보드판 위에서 플레이하며 샤인을 많이 모아 파티 스타가 되세요!
column5: 在棋盘上冒险，收集最多的太阳，成为超级巨星吧！
column6: 在棋盤上冒險，收集最多的太陽，成為超級巨星吧！
column7: パーティーを遊ぶことができます。シャインを集めてパーティースターになろう!
column8: Сыграйте в настолку, находите Шайни и станьте героем вечеринки

column2: Play and enjoy all the minigames!
column6: 玩和享受所有的小遊戲吧！
column7: ミニゲームをプレイすることができます。

column2: Different minigames packed together in all sorts of whacky ways!
column3: ¡Diferentes minijuegos agrupados en todo tipo de maneras descabelladas!
column5: 各种奇怪规则下的小游戏挑战！
column6: 各種小遊戲以各種奇怪的方式組合在一起！
column7: お題の制約がついたミニゲームをクリアしていきます。
column8: Различные миниигры собраны вместе в самых разных испытаниях

column2: Buy all sorts of different things to spice up the game
column3: ¡Compra diferentes artículos para animar el juego!
column4: 게임을 여러분의 입맛대로 바꿔줄 다양한 아이템을 여기서 구매하세요!
column5: 购买不同道具来获得更多游戏趣味。
column6: 購買不同的道具來為遊戲增添趣味。
column7: スキンやステージ、トライアルやミニゲームを購入することができます。
column8: Покупайте различные вещи чтобы разнообразить игру

column2: All the trophies you've earned are stored here!
column3: ¡Todos los trofeos que has conseguido se guardan aquí!
column4: 여러분이 얻은 모든 트로피는 여기서 보실 수 있습니다!
column5: 这里会展示你获得的所有奖杯！
column6: 您獲得的所有獎盃都存放在這裡！
column7: 今までに獲得したトロフィーを見ることができます。
column8: Все трофеи, заработанные вами, будут храниться здесь

column2: Would you like to hear about this board?
column5: 你想要了解这张地图的介绍吗？
column6: 你想要了解這張地圖的介紹嗎？
column7: このステージについて説明を聞きますか？
column8: Хотели бы вы узнать об этой доске?

column2: Welcome to the island! There's pretty much only ocean surrounding it. But it's still pretty nice!
column3: ¡Bienvenidos a la Isla!. Prácticamente solo hay mar rodeándola, ¡Pero sigue siendo bastante agradable!
column4: 섬에 오신것을 환영합니다! 주변에 보이는게 딱히 바다밖에 없지만, 그래도 꽤 괜찮은 곳이네요!
column5: 欢迎来到耀西岛！这里四处环海，风景优美！
column6: 歡迎來到耀西島上！它周圍幾乎只有海洋。但它仍然很不 錯！
column7: アイランドへようこそ! ここは海に囲まれており最高の場所です!
column8: Добро пожаловать на остров! Правда вокруг него лишь океан, но он все равно довольно неплох!

column2: This board has a 3 turn cycle between day and night.
column3: Este tablero tiene un ciclo de 3 turnos entre día y noche.
column5: 地图每三个回合切换昼夜。
column6: 這張地圖每三個回合後會切換白天和黑夜。
column7: このステージは、昼と夜が3ターンずつで入れ替わります。
column8: Это доска имеет цикл в 3 хода по смене дня и ночи.

column2: At day you can use the Shop but can't use the Blackhole. At night you can use the Blackhole but can't use the Shop.
column3: Durante el día puedes usar la Tienda, pero no puedes usar el Agujero Negro. Y, durante la noche, puedes usar el Agujero negro, pero no la Tienda.
column4: 낮에는 상점을 이용할 수 있지만 블랙홀을 사용하지 못하고, 반대로 밤에는 블랙홀이 사용 가능하지만 상점을 이용하지 못합니다.
column5: 在白天你可以进入商店但是不能使用黑洞。在晚上你可以使用黑洞但是不能进入商店。
column6: 在白天你可以進入商店但是不能使用黑洞。在晚上你 可以使用黑洞但是不能進入商店。
column7: 昼間はショップを利用することができますが、ブラックホールは使うことができません。夜は反対にブラックホールが使えますが、ショップは利用できません。
column8: Когда на улице день вы можете использовать Магазин, однако не можете использовать Черную Дыру. Ночью же наоборот, вы можете использовать Черную Дыру, но не Магазин.

column2: Also, the Shine will have a random price at night. It can be {40 coins} {30 coins} {10 coins} and {0 coins}! All Shines will stay at this price for the rest of the turn.
column3: Cuando es un turno nocturno, el Sol tendrá un precio aleatorio. Puede ser {50 coins}, {40 coins}, {30 coins}, {10 coins}, ¡Y {0 coins}!. Tendrá ese precio durante el resto del turno.
column4: 밤에는 샤인의 가격이 무작위 하게 바뀝니다. 가격은 {50 coins} {40 coins} {30 coins} {10 coins}, 심지어 {0 coins}이 될 수 있습니다! 남은 턴 동안 가격은 동일하게 유지됩니다.
column5: 并且太阳在晚上的价格将随机为 {40 coins} {30 coins} {10 coins} 或 {0 coins} ！每回合太阳的价格都是固定的。
column6: 當輪到晚上時，太陽將有一個隨機價格，可以是{40  coins} {30 coins} {10 coins} 或 {0 coins}！每回合太陽 的價格都是固定的。
column7: また、シャインの値段は夜間毎でランダムになり、{40 coins} {30 coins} {10 coins} {0 coins}のいずれかで購入できます!
column8: Ночью во время хода у Шайни будет случайная цена. Она может стоит как  {40 coins} {30 coins} {10 coins} так и вовсе {0 coins}! Цена Шайни сохраняется во время всего хода.

column2: Welcome! My it's really hot in here... hope you don't mind the heat too much!
column3: ¡Bienvenidos! Vaya, sí que hace calor aquí... ¡Espero no les moleste mucho el calor!
column5: 欢迎！天气好热啊……希望你没有中暑！
column6: 歡迎！我的天，這裡真的很熱……希望您不要太介意 高溫！
column7: ようこそ! ここは本当に暑いです…。暑さを気にしないでください!
column8: Добро пожаловать! О божечки, тут довольно жарко... надеюсь вас это не сильно побеспокоит.

column2: Two Shines are present on this board. The goal is to purchase the correct Shine! One of them is fake and the other is real. You won't know until you pay for it!
column3: Dos Soles se mostrarán en este tablero. La meta será comprar el Sol correcto, uno de ellos es falso y el otro es real. ¡No sabrás cuál es cual hasta que compres uno de ellos!
column4: 이 보드에는 샤인이 두개가 있습니다. 올바른 샤인을 구매하는것이 여러분의 목표입니다! 둘 중 하나는 진짜고 하나는 가짜입니다만, 구매하기 전까진 구분을 못한답니다!
column5: 这张地图可以同时存在两个太阳，其中一个是真的一个是假的。你的目标是购买真的太阳，但是在你购买之前无法确认真假。
column6: 這張地圖同時存在兩個太陽，其中有一個是真的有一 個是假的。你的目標是購買真的太陽，但是在你購買 之前你無法確認真假。
column8: На этой доске есть два Шайни. Цель доски это купить правильную Шайни! Одна из Шайни поддельная, а другая реальная. Но, чтобы узнать настоящая она или нет вы должны будете ее купить!

column2: Once the fake Shine is discovered the other one is guaranteed to be real. If the real one is obtained, the fake one will disappear and two more Shines will spawn.
column3: Una vez que el Sol falso fue encontrado está asegurado que el otro sea el real. Si el real es obtenido primero, el falso desaperecerá y reaparecerán dos Soles más.
column4: 만약 가짜 샤인이 밝혀진다면 남은 하나는 진짜로 확정됩니다. 만약 진짜 샤인을 누가 획득한다면, 가짜 샤인은 사라지고 샤인 2개가 더 나타납니다.
column5: 当有人购买了假太阳后，剩下的那个太阳一定是真的。如果有人购买了真的太阳，假的太阳将会消失，然后重新生成一对新的真假太阳。
column6: 一旦有人發現假的太陽，就可以保證另一個是真的。  如果有人購買了真的太陽，假的太陽就會消失，並且 會另外生成一對新的真假太陽。
column8: Когда поддельная Шайни обнаружена, другая Шайни гарантированно будет верной. Если правильная Шайни была выбрана изначально, то поддельная также исчезнет, и вместо них появятся две новых Шайни.

column2: Welcome to drawings everywhere! Let's hope for no puzzle shenanigans.
column8: Добро пожаловать в нарисованный мир! Надеюсь здесь не будет никаких странных пазлов.

column2: There's some puzzle blocks on some paths, those blocks are toggled everytime you cross them.
column8: Здесь есть несколько пазловых блоков на некоторыхпутях, они активируются каждый раз когда вы проходите по ним.

column2: There's a block pair for Shines, one for Spaces, and another for Shops. Depending on what the text says on the rightmost block, that's the thing it's gonna apply.
column8: Есть пара блоков специально для Шайни, также один для каждой Клетки, и другой для Магазинов. В зависимости от того что написано на самом правом блоке, то будет применено.

column2: The text from that block changes every turn, so be careful!
column8: Каждый ход эти блоки меняют свой текст, так что будьте осторожны.

column2: Welcome to the world of Pokemon! Gotta catch 'em all!
column3: ¡Bienvenido al mundo de los Pokémon! ¡Atrápalos a todos!
column4: 포켓몬 세계에 온 것을 환영합니다! 우리 모두의 꿈은 포켓몬 마스터!
column5: 欢迎来到宝可梦大陆！我抓到了！
column6: 歡迎來到神奇寶貝大陸！需要把他們全都抓到！
column8: Добро пожаловать в мир Покемонов! Поймай их всех!

column2: Here your objective is to fight Pokemon, and win their Shines.
column3: Aquí tu objetivo es combatir contra pokemones y conseguir sus Soles.
column4: 이 보드의 주 목표는 포켓몬과 배틀을 하여 샤인을 얻는 것입니다,
column5: 你的目标是和精灵战斗，并且赢取他们的太阳。
column6: 你的目標是和神奇寶貝戰鬥，並贏取他們的太陽。
column8: На этой доске цель состоит в том чтобы сражаться с Покемонами и выигрывать у них Шайни.

column2: When you pass over a Pokemon Space, you will have the option to catch that Pokemon for {15 coins} or to battle it.
column3: Cuando pases sobre una casilla Pokémon tendrás la opción de capturar tal Pokémon por {15 coins} o combatir contra él.
column4: 포켓몬이 있는 칸을 지나가게 된다면, {15 coins}을 지불하고 포켓몬을 잡거나, 배틀을 할 수 있습니다.
column5: 每当你路过一只精灵，你可以选择花费 {15 coins} 捕获它，或者和它战斗。
column8: Каждый раз когда вы проходите через Клетку с Покемоном, у вас будет опция как поймать его {15 coins}, либо же сразиться с ним.

column2: If you win against a Pokemon that has a Shine, you'll obtain it. If you win against a Pokemon with no Shine, it'll give you {10 coins}. If you lose however, you'll lose {10 coins}.
column3: Si ganas contra un Pokémon que tiene un Sol, lo obtendrás. Si ganas contra un Pokémon sin Sol, te dará {10 coins}. En cambio si pierdes, se llevará {10 coins}.
column4: 샤인을 갖고 있는 포켓몬과 배틀해서 이긴다면, 샤인을 얻을 수 있습니다. 샤인을 갖고있지 않은 포켓몬을 상대로 이긴다면, {10 coins}을 얻습니다. 하지만 만약 배틀에서 지게된다면, {10 coins}을 잃게됩니다.
column5: 如果你战胜了一只携带太阳的精灵，你就会获得它的太阳。如果你战胜了一只没有携带太阳的精灵，你会获得 {10 coins} 。反之如果你输了，你会失去 {10 coins} 。
column8: Если вы победите в битве Покемона, у которого был Шайни, вы получите его Шайни. Если же у Покемона не было Шайни, то тот даст вам {10 coins}. При пройгрыше, вы потеряете {10 coins}.

column2: Certain Pokemon types are more effective against others.\nThe hierarchy goes as follows: Water -> Fire -> Grass -> Water.
column3: Ciertos tipos de Pokémon son más efectivos contra otros.\nEl orden de efectividad es la siguiente: Agua -> Fuego -> Planta -> Agua.
column4: 포켓몬의 각 타입은 서로 상성이 있습니다.\n 상성은 다음과 같습니다 : 물 -> 불 -> 풀 ->물.
column5: 精灵属性存在克制关系。水系克制火系，火系克制草系，草系克制水系。
column8: Эффективность Покемона зависит от типов Покемонов, что учавствуют в битве. \nИерархия типов покемонов: Водянной -> Огненный -> Травянной -> Водянной

column2: If you have a favorable Pokemon type, your chances of winning are 90%. If you have the same type it's 50%. Otherwise it's 15%.
column3: Si tienes un Pokémon de tipo favorable, tus chances de ganar son altas, si son del mismo tipo, es un 50/50. Caso contrario las chances son muy bajas.
column4: 만약 상성이 좋은 포켓몬을 지니고 있다면, 승리할 확률이 매우 높습니다. 동일 타입끼리는 확률이 반반이고, 상성이 좋지 않다면 확률이 매우 낮습니다.
column5: 如果你的精灵拥有有利的属性，你获胜的概率是90%。如果你的精灵是相同属性，获胜概率是50%。如果你的精灵是不利的属性，你有85%的概率输掉。
column8: Если тип вашего Покемона выше по иерархии, то ваши шансы на победу гораздо выше. Если типы Покемонов одинаковы то шансы пятьдесят на пятьдесят. Если ваш Покемон слабее по типу, то шансы на победу очень низки.

column2: Now go and become a real Pokemon trainer!
column3: ¡Ahora ve y conviértete en un genuino entrenador Pokémon!
column5: 那么现在就出发成为真正的精灵训练家吧！
column8: Теперь же вперед, станьте настоящим Покетренером!

column2: Welcome to your dreams! Is this how your dreams look like? That's LSD stuff right there.
column3: ¡Bienvenido a tus sueños! ¿Es así cómo se ven? Sí que tenemos material de LSD justo aquí.
column4: 여러분의 꿈속으로 들어오신것을 환영합니다! 이게 여러분의 꿈의 모습인가요? LSD라도 한 것 마냥 생겨먹었네요.

column2: Here you need to reach the Shine like usual. The difference is that there are some teleports scattered throughout the board.
column3: Aquí solo necesitas alcanzar el Sol como lo es normalmente. La diferencia es que hay algunos teletransportadores esparcidos a través del tablero.

column2: Every pair of teleporters are connected, you gotta remember where each one leads to!
column3: Cada par de teletransportadores están conectados. ¡Tendrás que recordar hacia dónde lleva cuál!

column2: Welcome to Hyrule! In the peaceful Kakariko Village no less.
column3: ¡Bienvenido a Hyrule! Nada menos que el pacífico Pueblo Kakarito.

column2: This board has a unique thing going on. It spawns three Shines instead of only one.\nSo what's the deal you say?
column3: Este tablero tiene algo único. Aparecerán tres Soles en vez de uno solo.\n¿Entonces que sucede con esto?

column2: When a new turn starts, there's a chance the board changes to the Dark World or back to the Light World.
column3: Cuando un nuevo turno comience, hay una posibilidad de que tablero cambie al Mundo Oscuro o regresar al Mundo Luminoso.

column2: In the Light World everything works as you normally expect.
column3: En el Mundo Luminoso todo funciona normalmente, nada del otro mundo.

column2: In the Dark World all the Shines become Evil Shines. They take away one Shine from you if you have one, or {20 coins} if you don't.
column3: En cambio en el Mundo Oscuro, los Soles se convierten en Soles Malignos. Te quitarán un Sol o {20 coins} si no tienes una.

column2: So be careful and try to avoid them as much as you can!
column3: ¡Así que mantente alerta e intenta evitarlos a toda costa!

column2: Welcome to the insanity! It's very interesting to be here in outer space.
column3: ¡Bienvenido a la locura! Es muy interesante estar aquí, en el espacio exterior.
column8: Добро пожаловать в безумие! Очень интересно быть здесь, в открытом космосе.

column2: This is a linear board, with only a single Shine. Your goal is to reach it fast!
column3: Este es un tablero lineal con solo un único Sol. Tu meta será llegar a ella lo más rápido que puedas.
column8: Это линейная доска с одним Шайни. Твоя цель достичь этого быстро!

column2: Why fast you ask? Because everytime someone buys a Shine the total cost goes up by {5 coins}! Starting from {10 coins}.
column3: ¿Y por qué rápido? Porque cada vez que alguien consigue un Sol, el precio irá incrementando en {5 coins}. Iniciando desde {10 coins}.
column8: Ты спросишь почему быстро? Потому что каждый раз когда кто-то покупает Шайни стоимость поднимается на {5 coins}! Начиная с {10 coins}.

column2: Welcome to everyone versus the world!
column8: Добро пожаловать во всё против мира

column2: You gotta be careful! There's a spooky Ghost roaming around! When it reaches you or you reach it, it takes a Shine away!
column3: ¡Debes tener cuidado! ¡Hay un Fantasma merodeando alrededor! Cuando él te alcanza o tú lo alcanzas, ¡Te arrebatará un Sol!
column8: Ты должен быть осторожным! здесь вокруг бродит страшный призрак! Если он дойтёт до вас или вы до него, то он заберёт твой Шайни!

column2: Plan your route accordingly and try to avoid Ghost at all costs while you collect Shines!
column3: ¡Planea tu ruta con cuidado e intenta evitar al fantasma a toda costa mientras recolectas Soles!
column8: Планируй свой маршрут и пытайтесь избегать призрака всей ценой пока вы будете собирать Шайни!

column2: Alright. Then let's choose the turns!
column3: Muy bien, eligamos el orden de turnos.
column5: 好的。现在让我们来决定行动顺序！
column6: 好的。現在讓我們來決定順序！

column2: Let's give each one {10 coins} to start.
column3: Les daremos {10 coins} a cada uno para iniciar.
column5: 每位玩家的初始资金为 {10 coins} 。
column6: 讓我們在開始給每個人 {10 coins}。
column8: Давай дадим каждому {10 coins} для начала.

column2: Let's see where the Shine is gonna end up...
column6: 讓我們看看太陽的位置會在......
column7: シャインがどこに出現するか見てみましょう…

column2: Do you wanna buy a Shine?
column5: 你想要购买这个太阳吗？
column6: 你想要購買這個太陽嗎？
column7: シャインを購入しますか?

column2: Here you go! The Shine is yours!
column5: 好的！这个太阳是你的了！
column6: 好的！這個太陽是你的了！
column7: どうぞ!これでシャインはあなたの物です!
いいですね! どうぞ!

column2: You were starting to worry me for a second!
column5: 这会儿你有点让我担心了！
column6: 你開始讓我擔心一秒鐘了！
column8: Ты начал меня беспокоить на секунду!

column2: Are you really sure you don't want it?
column6: 你真的確定你不需要它嗎？
column7: 本当によろしいですか?
column8: Ты действительно уверен что не хочешь этого?

column2: Well too bad then, I hope next time you change your mind.
column3: Qué lástima, espero que lo pienses mejor la proxima vez.
column5: 太遗憾了。希望下次你会改变主意。

column3: DeDeDe mostrará una secuencia de movimientos que deben ejecutar. Una vez realizada correctamente, !añadan una acción extra para el siguiente jugador! Tengan en cuenta que no podrán repetir el mismo movimiento dos veces seguidas.
column4: 디디디 대왕이 여러분이 따라해야할 동작 4개를 보여줄겁니다. 만약 성공적으로 따라하게 된다면, 동작 하나를 추가해서 다음 플레이어에게 넘길 수 있습니다. 단, 같은 동작을 연속으로 하지 못하는 점 유의해주세요.
column5: 你需要模仿帝帝帝大王展示的连续四个动作。每成功做完一组可以给下一位玩家增加一个动作！但要注意，你不能连续两次做同一个动作。

column2: {Left key}{Down key}{Right key} Direction\n{Jump key} Jump\n{Shoot key} Shoot

column5: {Left key}{Down key}{Right key} 方向\n{Jump key} 跳跃\n{Shoot key} 射击

column2:
A platform that increases speed overtime
is ascending the tower!
Avoid the spikes at all costs and be
the last one standing!
column4: 여러분은 계속해서 빨라지는 플랫폼을 타고 탑을 올라야 합니다!!\n가시를 피해 마지막까지 살아남으세요!
column5:
一个逐渐加速的平台
正在朝着塔的顶端上升！
尽你所能躲开所有的刺
成为站到最后的那个人！

column2: Don't let that intimidating ghost see you moving, stop if it faces you!\nIf it's about to turn around it'll laugh and an exclamation mark will appear above its head.
column5: 不要让那个恐怖的幽灵看到你移动，在它看向你的时候停下来！\n它在要转身之前会笑，并且头上会出现一个感叹号。

column2:
A set of items are above the pedestals.
Remember the place of each item before
the earthquake strikes!
Put them all back in the correct place.
column5:
每个底座上都有一个道具。
你需要在地震来临之前
记住所有道具的位置！
之后你需要把它们放回原来的位置。

column7: マンションからの脱出

column2:
You've been trapped in the attic of an old
mansion!
Be the first to escape!
Find all the doors that lead downstairs.
column5: 你被困在了一个老旧的公馆的顶楼！\n尝试第一个逃脱！\n寻找每一个通往下一层的房间。

column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Up key} 开门

{Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ

column5: 我的评价是 0/10 这里有太多错误了！\n你需要计算上方指示颜色错误虫的数量。最接近正确答案的玩家获胜。

column7: {Left key}{Right key} 数字を変える

column2: These blocks break upon anything landing on it. Be careful where you stand to be the last one alive!
column5: 这些砖块一碰就碎！注意你的脚下，成为活到最后的那个人！
{Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ

column5: 每个宝箱都有不同数目的金币，在它们快速换位后，找到最多金币的那个并且第一个捡起来！一共三个回合，宝箱的交换速度会越来越快。

column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Up key} 捡起宝箱

column5: 看到这个可爱的史莱姆了吗！\n我觉得你想要惹火它不是吗？你可以向它射击，但是要注意！它有可能会原谅你，也可能会杀了你。所以努力成为活到最后的那个人吧。

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Move\n{Jump key} Jump\n{Shoot key} Shoot
column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃\n{Shoot key} 射击
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ\n{Shoot key} ショット
ロケットイグニッション

column5: 这是一个火箭竞赛，所有人都要互相竞争，到处瞄准并射击。每个人起始有3点血，活到最后的人获胜！

column2:
{Left key}{Right key} Turn
{Up key} Accelerate Forward
{Down key} Accelerate Backwards
{Shoot key} Shoot
column5:

{Left key}{Right key} 回転
{Up key} 進行方向に進む
{Down key} 逆方向に進む

column5: 试着不要绕晕！\n收集所有你的颜色的硬币。每当你接触一个传送门，你的所有操作都会被打乱，所以你要重新找出每个按键对应什么操作。

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Move\n{Jump key} Flip Gravity\n{Left key}{Up key}{Down key}{Right key}{Jump key} After Shuffle
column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 反重力\n{Left key}{Up key}{Down key}{Right key}{Jump key} 被打乱后

column2: Break the targets! You have 6 bullets to do so. Red gives you 1 point, blue 2 points, and yellow 3 points.
column5: 破坏那些靶子！你一共可以使用六发子弹，红色靶子是1分，蓝色靶子是2分，黄色靶子是3分。

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Move\n{Jump key} Jump\n{Shoot key} Shoot
column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃\n{Shoot key} 射击
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ\n{Shoot key} ショット

column2: Time to dodge the bullets! Blue bullets are water and you can jump infinitely while in them, they also refresh your double jump. Black and white bullets kill you, avoid them! After a while bouncing cherries spawn on the bottom so avoid them too!
column5: 现在是躲子弹时间！蓝色子弹是水，你可以在水里无限跳，且在水中会重置你的二段跳。黑白相间的子弹碰到会死，躲开它们！一段时间后屏幕下方会出现樱桃在屏幕间不断反弹，你同样需要躲开。
{Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ

column2: Grab as many key drawings as possible. Green gives 1 point, yellow gives 2 points and red gives 3 points. Make use of the blocks below you, if they're green and you jump they're gonna launch you upwards.
column5: 尽你所能收集更多的钥匙图画，绿色是1分，黄色是2分，红色是3分。当你踩在绿色的砖上跳跃时你会被发射得很高。
{Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ

column2: Time for bubble race! It's hard to control, don't try going too fast! If you hit a spike you're unable to move for a bit. Take into account the better you're doing in the race the longer you have to wait. 3 laps to win!
column5: 现在是泡泡赛跑时间！它很难控制所以不要飞的太快！如果你碰到刺了你会在一段时间内不能移动。你在赛跑中做的越好需要等待的时间越长。先绕完三圈的玩家获胜！
{Left key}{Up key}{Down key}{Right key} 移动
column7: {Left key}{Up key}{Down key}{Right key} 移動

column2: I hope you prepared your parachute, because you're falling fast! While you're at it, make sure to touch the yellow saves. Red circles gives you 1 point and green circles gives you 2 points. The one with the most points wins!
column5: 我希望你准备好了降落伞，因为你在下落。在这段时间里，确保你碰到黄色的存档，中心红圈是1分，绿圈是2分。获得最高分的玩家获胜！
{Left key}{Up key}{Down key}{Right key} 移动
column7: {Left key}{Up key}{Down key}{Right key} 移動

column2: Mini-golf time! Prepare your shot carefully. The ball needs to land in the flag hole for a perfect 100 score. If it doesn't, you get points based on how close you were, and if you fall off no points for you!
column5: 现在是迷你高尔夫时间！仔细瞄准这一杆。你必须将高尔夫球打进洞以获得满分100分。如果没有进洞，你将根据落点和洞的距离得分，如果你掉出场外则是0分！

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Adjust Angle\n{Jump key} Use Angle/Use Force\n{Shoot key} Cancel Angle
column5: {Left key}{Right key} 调整角度\n{Jump key} 使用角度/使用力度\n{Shoot key} 取消角度
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 角度の調整\n{Jump key} 角度を決定/ショット\n{Shoot key} 角度を決めなおす

column2: The Pac-Man invasion is upon us... pay attention to all the safe trajectories, or else you'll get killed! The last one standing wins!
column5: 吃豆人入侵了……注意每一条安全轨道，否则你就会被杀掉！活到最后的玩家获胜！

column7: {Left key}{Right key} 場所を移動する

column2: Sledge in the snow couldn't be left out! But there's obstacles in the way! Jump to avoid the spikes and shoot to destroy the trees and candies and toggle the colored blocks. First to reach the goal wins!
column5: 这里当然少不了雪橇！但是路上会有很多障碍物！跳跃躲避刺，射击破坏树和糖果，同时切换彩色砖块。第一个到达终点的玩家获胜！
{Jump key} 跳跃\n{Shoot key} 射击/切换
column7: {Jump key} ジャンプ\n{Shoot key} ショット/切り替え

column5: 你的任务是消灭{Color}多人队伍{Color}，在下方顶砖以从三种弹幕类型中选择一种用来攻击。每种攻击都是不一样的！

column2: Avoid the cherries at all costs! The {Color}Solo Player{Color} is trying to eliminate you with their arsenal of cherries! Pay attention to which block they activate.
column5: 尽你所能躲避樱桃弹幕！{Color}单人玩家{Color}会尝试用樱桃武器消灭你们！时刻注意对方激活了哪种弹幕。
{Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ

column5: 那个传送带看起来很有用，触碰按钮改变传送带的方向。频繁切换方向以扰乱{Color}多人队伍{Color}并消灭他们！

column2: That conveyor is fast, beware! The {Color}Solo Player{Color} is gonna constantly change the conveyor's direction, pay attention and survive!
column5: 传送带很快，要小心！{Color}单人玩家{Color}将会频繁切换传送带的方向，集中注意力并活下来！

one of your opponents, their block
falls apart.

column5:
从1到3选一个数字。
如果你选到了和某一个对手
相同的数字，其砖块

Pick a number between 1 and 3.

If that number is the same as the one that
{Color}Solo Player{Color} picked, then your
block breaks.

从1到3选一个数字。

column7: {Left key}{Up key}{Down key}{Right key}{Jump key}{Shoot key} 操作

column5: 尽你所能躲掉传送门！你的目标是将三个灰色砖块推到最左边以抵达刺并自杀。{Color}多人队伍{Color}会向上发射传送门来阻止你。

column5: {Color}单人玩家{Color}正在尝试自杀，你需要阻止他！持续向上发射传送门来送他回到起点以阻止他推过全部三个灰色砖块！

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Move\n{Color}Team Players{Color}\n{Shoot key} Shoot Warp

column2: The {Color}Team Players{Color} are hunting you, throw them off by constantly jumping around and try not to fall off the blocks!
column5: {Color}多人队伍{Color}正在猎杀你，来回跳跃以甩开他们并且避免掉出屏幕！

column2: The {Color}Solo Player{Color} is trying to get away. Corner them, aim, and then shoot to kill!
column5: {Color}单人玩家{Color}正在尝试逃离，包抄他，瞄准，射击，击杀之！

column2: Destroy all the {Color}Team Players{Color}' blocks by shooting at them. But don't destroy the empty blocks or else they're gonna have more freedom to move!
column5: 射击破坏所有{Color}多人队伍{Color}的砖块。尽量避免破坏空的砖块，否则他们会获得更多躲避空间！

column2: Don't get hit by the {Color}Solo Player{Color}'s laser! Move around to dodge it, but don't get trapped in between two empty blocks or you're gonna be unable to escape!
column5: 不要被{Color}单人玩家{Color}的镭射打到！四处移动躲避之，但要避免被困在两个空的砖块中间，否则你将无路可逃！

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Move\n{Color}Solo Player{Color}:\n{Shoot key} Shoot
column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Color}单人玩家{Color}：\n{Shoot key} 射击
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Color}Solo Player{Color}:\n{Shoot key} ショット

column2: Choose which door you wanna hide in at the start. But try to trick the {Color}Team Players{Color} by just wandering around. After each round the doors the others chose are gonna be locked. It's three rounds to win!
column5: 选择你要躲藏的门。四处徘徊以迷惑{Color}多人队伍{Color}。每回合被对方选中的门都会上锁。成功躲藏三回合以获胜！

column2: The {Color}Solo Player{Color} will choose one of the doors. Try to guess which door they chose, if you fail to find them the door you chose is gonna lock up! Try to find them before three rounds pass.
column5: {Color}单人玩家{Color}会选择其中一个门。请猜测其选择的门，如果你猜错了，被你选中的门会上锁！请在三回合内抓住他。

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Move\n{Jump key} Jump Infinitely\n{Up key} Pick Door
column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 无限跳跃\n{Up key} 选择门
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} 無限ジャンプ\n{Up key} ドアを選ぶ

column2: That's a very bad house! Don't let the cherries touch you. The house is being controlled by the {Color}Team Players{Color}, survive and wait for the timer to expire.
column3: Esa es una casa muy mala! No dejes que las cerezas te toquen, la casa esta siendo controlada por el {Color}Equipo Rival{Color}, sobrevive hasta que el reloj llegue a cero.
column5: 这是个非常讨厌的小屋！不要让樱桃碰到你，{Color}多人队伍{Color}正在控制小屋，在时限内活下来。

column2: You control the bad house, but each member of the team only has control of a single action. Cooperate and kill the {Color}Solo Player{Color} before the time runs out!
column3: Tu controlaras la casa mala, pero cada miembro solo tendra una unica accion para controlar. Cooperen y maten al {Color}Solo Player{Color} antes de que termine el tiempo
column5: 你们能控制这个讨厌的小屋，但队伍里每个成员只能控制一种行动。在时限内合作并猎杀{Color}单人玩家{Color}！
{Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ

column2: Quick! You have to assemble your team spike. It's divided into two pieces, you and your teammate must each find one of the pieces and then reunite! Make sure to grab a piece of your team's color!
column5: 快！你们必须组装好队伍的刺。它被分成了两部分，你和你的队友必须分别找到其中一部分然后组装起来！确保你拿的是队伍的颜色！

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Move\n{Jump key} Jump Infinitely
column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 无限跳跃
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} 無限ジャンプ

column2: Fruits are falling from the tree, catch as many as you can to win! Big fruits give 1 point, medium fruits give 2 points, and small fruits give 3 points. Don't catch the spiky Gordos or 1 point will be taken away.
column5: 树上会掉下水果，尽你所能接到更多以获胜！大号水果给1分，中号水果给2分，小号水果给3分。不要接到刺球否则会被扣除1分。

column2: Compete to press more buttons than the other team! Once the button highlights red you have to be quick and shoot it.
column5: 你要和另一支队伍竞争按按钮的次数！当按钮变红以后你需要以最快的速度射击之。

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Move\n{Jump key} Jump Infinitely\n{Shoot key} Shoot
column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 无限跳跃\n{Shoot key} 射击
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} 無限ジャンプ\n{Shoot key} ショット

column2:
Each team must assemble
their squares,
put both of them in the correct orientation
to fit them!
Players control half a square each.
column5:
每个队伍都需要组装
他们的正方形，
将两个碎片都转到正确的角度
以组装他们！
每个玩家控制一个碎片。

column2: That's a ton of colors... cooperate with your teammate to find the only two squares that are exactly the same. 4 rounds to win!
column5: 这里有很多颜色……和队友合作找到唯一的一对相同的方块。配对4次以获胜！

column2: {Left key}{Up key}{Down key}{Right key} Move\n{Jump key} Select/Deselect Square

column2: Avoid the fireballs! Survive longer than the other team. The upper player bounces around a spring, the bottom player controls the spring. If either on the team die the fireballs start shooting faster!
column5: 躲开那些火球！你要比另一支队伍存活更久。上方的玩家会在弹簧上弹跳，下方的玩家则是要控制弹簧。当队伍中有一人死亡时火球会发射得更快！
{Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ

column2: Be the first duo to reach the end. Help your teammate to overcome each section. First you need to press buttons by shooting. Then finding the correct warp to advance. And finally inflate the leek to win!
column5: 你们要成为第一对到达终点的拍档。帮助你的队友打通道路。首先你需要射击按钮。随后找到正确的传送门前进。最后让大葱长大以获胜！

column2: {Left key}{Right key} Move\n{Jump key} Jump\n{Shoot key} Shoot
column5: {Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃\n{Shoot key} 射击

column2: Pay attention! Be the fastest shooter in the Old West. Once you see the exclamation mark, shoot as fast as you can. Whoever shoots faster wins 1 point. Reach 5 points to win.
column5: 注意！你要成为西部决斗中最快的枪手。当你看到感叹号时，以最快的速度射击。射击更快的玩家赢得1分。累计达到5分的一方获胜。

column2: This is soccer, everyone knows the rules! Score 5 points in order to win. If you touch the ball it shoots off based on the direction you're looking, so careful with that!
column5: 这就是足球，大家都知道规则！累计达到5分以获胜。当你碰到球的时候它会被射到你面对的方向，要小心！
{Left key}{Right key} 移动\n{Jump key} 跳跃
column7: {Left key}{Right key} 移動\n{Jump key} ジャンプ

column2: Whac-a-mole idol edition! Hit as many idols, gently of course, as you can. The team that hits more idols wins!
column5: 这是打地鼠的偶像版本！尽你所能敲击更多的偶像，当然，要轻轻地。敲到更多偶像的队伍获胜！

column2: You obtained 10 Shines!\nI can do more!

column5: 你获得了10个太阳！\n我可以做得更好！

column2: You're gonna obtain something shiny sooner or later.
column3: Tarde o temprano obtendrás el brillo.
column7: 光り輝くものを集めてみよう。

column2: You obtained 50 Shines!\nBut is it really enough?
column5: 你获得了50个太阳！\n但你满足了吗？

column3: ¡Has obtenido 50 Soles!\nEso es una buena cantidad
column5: 你获得了100个太阳！\n这还真是个可观的数量。
我 要 更 加 闪 亮！！！

column3: ¡Has alcanzado las 100 monedas en una Fiesta!\n¿Que se siente ser rico?

column3: ¡Has perdido hasta tener 0 monedas un una Fiesta!\n Supongo que es hora de vivir en la calle.
column5: 你在派对中持有0枚金币……\n这下要睡大街上了。

column2: You don't wanna lose that many.
You got the same number for the place, Shines and Coins! You love seeing the same number!
column3: Tuviste el mismo numero para el puesto, Soles y Monedas! Te encanta ver el mismo número
column4: 순위, 샤인, 코인이 전부 같은 숫자를 나타내고 있네요!\n역시 숫자가 같아야 보기 좋죠?

column5: 嘿，我的一切都是同一个数字！

column3: Amigo Del Señor De La Noche

column4: 저기요, 그 빛나는 것 좀 치워줘요.

column3: ¡Has encontrado un cofre oculto!\nCada buen explorador encuentra sus tesoros! Espera... a lo mejor ha sido suerte
column4: 숨겨진 상자를 찾으셨습니다!\n모든 위대한 탐험가는 보물을 찾아낸다고 하죠! 근데 당신은...운이 좋았던 것 같네요.
column5: 你找到了一个隐藏宝箱！\n每个优秀的探险家都会找到宝藏！或者……也许你只是运气好？

column5: 这个格子上藏着些什么……我保证……

column2: You found a Shine within a Hidden Chest!?\nNow that's peak exploring... I mean luck right there.
column4: 숨겨진 상자에서 샤인을 찾으셨다고요!?\n당신 정말로 위대한 탐험- 이 아니라 운이 좋으셨네요.
column5: 你在隐藏宝箱中找到了一个太阳！？\n这可是世纪发现……我的意思是你的运气很好。

column2: Why couldn't this give me something shinier?
column4: 여기서 뭐 반짝이는게 나올 것 같지 않아?
column5: 这玩意为什么不能给我点更闪亮的东西？

column2: You landed on a Red space when having 0 Coins.\nWhat does it feel to be at -3 Coins?
column3: Has caido en una casilla roja mientras tenias 0 monedas.\n¿Que se siente tener -3 monedas?
column4: 코인 0개를 보유 중일 때 빨간 칸에 착지하셨네요.\n -3코인을 가지게 된 소감이 어떻나요?
column5: 你在没有金币的时候停在了红色格子。\n持有-3枚金币是什么感受？

column4: 여기서 더 잃을 순 없어! 멈춰!!
column5: 我不能失去更多了，快停下！

column2: You received a Blackhole or a Mirror from an item space!\nNow that's a handy item after so many Poisons!
column3: ¡Recibiste un Agujero Negro o Espejo desde una casilla de objeto!\n¡Eso si que son buenos items despues de obtener tanto Veneno!
column5: 你在道具格子获得了一个黑洞或者镜子！\n在那么多毒药之后终于有点有用的道具了！

column2: Heck yeah! I was getting tired of so many lame items in this space!\nThis is definitely better!
column5: 太好了！我已经受够这格子上的那些辣鸡道具了！\n这要好太多了！

column5: 你停在Guy格子上获得了100太阳！\n好 的！100 个 太 阳 让 我 拿 下！\n等等……我的太阳呢！！？？

column2: Even a bad guy can give you something shiny.
column5: 即使是个坏家伙也可以给你闪亮的东西。

column2: You received 1 coin landing on The Guy space...\nReally...? That's it...? Kinda hoping for a little bit more considering I had nothing...
column5: 你停在Guy格子上获得了1枚金币……\n真的……？就这……？还以为能得到更多，毕竟我已经一无所有……

column2: Even a bad guy can give you... something...?
column5: 即使是个坏家伙也可以给你一些……什么……？

column2: All of you landed on Red spaces.\nRed everywhere you see.
column5: 所有人都停在红色格子。\n你看现在到处都是红色。

column2: All of you landed on Green spaces.\nGreen everywhere you see.
column5: 所有人都停在绿色格子。\n你看现在到处都是绿色。

column2: All of you landed on different colored spaces.\nDifferent colors everywhere you see.
column5: 所有人都停在不同颜色的格子。\n你看现在到处都是不同颜色。

column2: You received a Shine in the last 5 turns event!\nThat was unexpected, the other players must be hating you right now!
column3: Obtuviste un Sol en el evento de Ultimos 5 turnos!\n¡Eso fue inesperado, los demas te deben estar odiando ahora mismo!
column5: 你在最后五回合事件中获得一个太阳！\n这还真是意料之外，其他玩家现在肯定恨死你了！

column2: I bet you weren't expecting to get that on the last 5 turns!
column5: 我觉得你不该在最后五回合得到那个！

column2: You landed on a blue space when all the blue spaces were red spaces!\nAt least you gained something while this mess was happening.
column5: 你在所有蓝色格子都变成红色格子的时候停在了蓝色格子上！\n至少你在这一团糟的时候获得了些什么。

column2: Landing on a good one while there's so many bad ones.
column5: 在到处都很糟糕的时候停在了一个好的位置。

column2: You used the Cellphone and said no.\nCalling the wrong number, happens from time to time.
column5: 你使用了手机但没完全使用。\n打错号码了，这是天天发生的事情。

column2: Woops, that's not the right number, my bad.
column5: 哎呀，这不是正确的号码，我的错。

column2: You used the Blackhole and said no.\nYeah there's a bunch of galaxies to call, it's only natural you'd get confused.
column5: 你使用了黑洞但没完全使用。\n是啊，有太多星系了，搞错也很正常嘛。

column2: Woops, that's not the right galaxy, my bad.
column5: 哎呀，这不是正确的星系，我的错。

column2: You rolled two identical numbers with Double Dice!\nMore rolling for me!

column2: Double the numbers, double the fun.
column5: 双倍的数字，双倍的惊喜。

column2: You rolled 25 or more with Triple Dice!\nJust casually going for a walk around the board, no big deal.
column3: ¡Has sacado 25 o mas con un Triple Dado!\nSimplemente un paseo por todo el tablero, nada nuevo.
column5: 你用三骰子累计掷出25点或以上！\n现在随随便便绕图一周也不是什么问题。

column2: Hey slow down a little bit!
You rolled 10 or less with a Triple Dice.\nI'm gonna reach the Shine, I swear...
column3: Has sacado 10 o menos con un Triple Dado.\nLlegare hasta el Sol, lo jiro...
column5: 你用三骰子累计掷出10点或以下！\n我会到达太阳的，我保证……

column2: I would've used a regular one if I knew this was gonna happen...
column3: Hubiera usado uno normal si sabia que esto pasaba...
column5: 若吾早知如此，就用个普通的了……

column2: You rolled three identical numbers with Triple Dice!\nI can't stop rolling!
column5: 你用三骰子掷出了三个一样的数字！\n我停不下来了！

column2: You used the Mirror when you didn't have enough Coins.\nNow both you and the Mirror are broke, congratulations!
column5: 你在身上没有足够金币的时候使用了镜子。\n现在你和镜子都破产了，恭喜！

column2: Now two things are broke by such use.
column5: 这么浪费，现在两样都坏掉了。

column2: You received a Night Shine for 0 Coins in the Island board!\nThat was a free trial, next time you won't be so lucky.
This one is on the house.
You bought a Night Shine for 40 Coins in the Island board.\nIt'd be best if you waited for a sale next time.
column3: Compraste un Sol Nocturno por 40 Monedas en el tablero Isla.\nSerá bueno que esperes a las ofertas para la próxima.

column2: Gimme full price! I ain't waiting for a hot sale.
column5: 我要全价！我并没有在等大甩卖。

column2: You used the Cellphone when it was night.\nSorry but the shop doesn't have night shifts.\nIt'd be best if you actually went during the day, thank you.
column5: 你在晚上使用了手机。\n抱歉，商店晚上不营业。\n如果你白天来就好了，谢谢。

column2: Pay attention to the customer support schedule.
column5: 请注意顾客服务的日程安排。

column2: You won without catching a Pokemon in the Pallet Town board!\nI thought your dream was to become a Pokemon trainer... where's your Pokemon then?
column5: 你在真新镇地图没有抓精灵并获胜！\n我还以为你的梦想是成为精灵训练家……但是你的精灵呢？

column2: You lost a Pokemon battle while having a favorable Pokemon in the Pallet Town board.\nWell that's some tough luck right there. Maybe try a different Pokemon next time.
column5: 你在真新镇地图使用克制对方的精灵但是输掉了战斗。\n看来你的运气不佳。下次换一只精灵试试吧。

column2: Water vs. Fire should be an easy win... right?
column5: 水系对付火系应该轻松获胜的……对吧？

column2: You won a Pokemon battle while not having a favorable Pokemon in the Pallet Town board.!\nI didn't think a fire attack against a water type was gonna work out. But I'm not complaining!
column5: 你在真新镇地图使用不利属性的精灵但是赢得了战斗！\n我不认为逆属性能够获胜。但我不会抱怨什么！

column2: Fire vs. Water could never work out... right?
column5: 火系对付水系应该不可能赢得……对吧？

column2: You used the Mirror in Dark World in the Hyrule board.\nDid you know you can't see your reflection in the dark?\nThen I wonder why you used this.
I wonder what my reflection looks like when it's dark.
You obtained a Tie in a minigame.\nWelp guess no one wins anything.
column5: 你在小游戏中平局。\n看起来没有人拿到任何东西。

column2: You died on the very first row of spikes in Tower Ascension.\nHaving the high ground wasn't appealing.
column5: 你在攀爬高塔中死于第一排刺。\n到达高层并没有吸引力。

column2: You went back after almost reaching the light in Haunted Forest.\nNow that's just showing off.
column5: 你在恐怖之森中即将到达出口的曙光时返回。\n现在是展现技术的时间。

column2: Spooky stuff ain't that scary for you.
column5: 阴森的东西对你来说并不恐怖。

column2: You scored a perfect 10 in Magic Memory.\nCan I borrow that memory of yours for a second?
column5: 你在魔法记忆中拿到满分10分。\n我能借你的记忆力一小会儿吗？

column2: How can you keep so many items in your head?
column5: 你是如何将如此多的道具装在脑子里的？

column2: You got all items wrong in Magic Memory...\nI bet you forget your house keys every time you go out, huh?
column5: 你在魔法记忆中把所有道具都放错了……\n我赌你每次出门都忘记带房子钥匙，是吧？

column2: You can't have that bad of a memory...
column5: 你不能记忆力如此之差吧……

column2: You chose only the correct doors in Mansion Escape.\nHoudini would be proud of you.
column5: 你在逃离公馆中只选择正确的门逃脱。\n胡迪尼会为你自豪的。

column2: You died to the top spikes in Unstable Blocks.\nWait, why? It's literally not moving.\nYou did it on purpose I swear.
column5: 你在易碎砖块中死于顶部的刺。\n等等，为什么？它可一点都没有动。\n我发誓你是故意的。

column2: Those are at the very top, that can't seriously happen.
column5: 它们在最高的地方，这没有道理发生。

column2: You scored 0 points by going for the empty chests in Crazy Chests.\nThose chests were kind of a scam, huh?
column5: 你在疯狂宝箱中全部选择空的宝箱得到0分。\n这些宝箱都是假的，是吗？

column2: Hey wait a minute... these chests are empty!
column5: 嘿，等一下……这些宝箱都是空的！

column2: You touched the slime in Slime Annoyer.\nIt's cute, I know, but it's deadly!
column5: 你在调戏史莱姆中碰到了史莱姆。\n它很可爱，我知道，可爱并致命！

column2: I know it's tempting, but it's not huggable.
column5: 我知道它很有吸引力，但它不可拥抱。

column2: You didn't receive a single hit in Rocket Ignition!\nAll those years of astronaut training in the morning finally paid off!
column5: 你在火箭发射中无伤！\n这些年早晨的宇航员训练终于得到了回报！

column2: You touched every warp in Dizzy Conundrum.\nStop! You're making me dizzy!
column5: 你在晕头转向中碰到了所有传送门。\n快停下！你让我头晕了！

column2: You never changed controls and won in Dizzy Conundrum!\nMy, you must really hate being dizzy.
column5: 你在晕头转向中在没有碰到任何传送门的情况下获胜！\n我的天你一定非常讨厌晕眩。

column2: You hit a yellow target first in Targetting Targets.\nWith that level of aiming you should be able to win everytime.
column5: 你在射击标靶中先打中了黄色的靶子。\n有这种瞄准水准你应该能百战百胜。

column2: You wasted all your bullets in Targeting Targets.\nThe point was to shoot targets and not walls, in case you didn't know.
column5: 你在射击标靶中浪费掉所有的子弹。\n告诉你目标是射击标靶而不是墙，免得你不知道。

column2: Wasting ammo to hit nothing, great.
column5: 浪费了弹药什么都没有打到，太好了。

column2: You didn't grab a single green key and won in Drawn Keys!\nGoing for the big prize keys here!
column5: 你在图画钥匙中在没有捡到任何一个绿色钥匙的情况下获胜！\n这里只要大奖的钥匙！

column2: You didn't touch a single spike and won in Bubble Derby!\nAll that Kamilia 3 speedrunning must've paid off, huh?
column5: 你在泡泡竞速中在没有碰到任何一个刺的情况下获胜！\n那些K3的速通总算有了回报，不是吗？

column2: You only touched green saves and won in Sky Diving!\nThat satisfaction to see the green circle after a long save, am I right?
column5: 你在空中跳伞中只碰到绿色的存档并获胜！\n在长存之后看到一个绿色的存档很满足，我对吗？

column2: I prefer the green circles for yellow boxes.
column5: 我更喜欢黄色箱子中的绿圈。

column2: You scored 99 points in Golf Course.\nHere hoping for the wind to barely move the ball, right?
column5: 你在高尔夫球场中获得99分。\n现在祈祷风把球微微吹动一下，对吧？

column2: Come on, man! The flag is right there!
column5: 干什么呀！旗子就在那里了！

column2: You won while not leaving the main island in Golf Course!\nToo lazy to do a normal shot, aren't you?
column5: 你在高尔夫球场中在没有离开起点小岛的情况下获胜！\n正常打球太累了，不是吗？

column2: I barely attempted to get to the flag and I still won.
column5: 我几乎没有打算打到旗子那里但还是赢了。

column2: You won by doing nothing in Waka Evasion!\nLuigi must be so proud of you right now.
column5: 你在躲避吃豆人中什么都没做就赢了！\n路易吉现在肯定为你而自豪。

column2: You jumped directly into the ceiling spikes in Conveyor Havoc.\nDid you think you could escape the conveyor by jumping? Think again.
column5: 你在传送带之劫中直接跳向头顶的刺。\n你觉得跳起来就能逃离传送带了吗？再好想想吧。

column2: Jump straight to victory! And by victory I mean death.
column5: 直接跳向“胜利”！“胜利”指的是死亡。

column2: You survived all 3 rounds with your team in Number Showdown.\nThat's teamwork for you! Or not?
column5: 你在猜数对决中三回合全队生还。\n这是你们的团队合作！或者不是？

column2: That was certainly some showdown teamwork.
You killed the whole team in the first round in Number Showdown.\nIn cold blood.
column5: 你在猜数对决的第一个回合杀光全队的成员。\n冷酷无情。

column2: You better not murder the showdown.
You didn't grab a single coin in Getting Coins.\nThe point is to collect them not to dodge them.
column5: 你在获得金币中没有拿到任何一枚硬币。\n目标是收集它们而不是躲避它们。

column2: There's a lot of coins, but I prefer being poor.
column5: 这里有很多金币，但我喜欢穷。

column2: You collected a red coin in Getting Coins!\nFINALLY! This red coin in G stage was really hard. Or wait... is this the wrong game?
column5: 你在获得金币中收集了一枚红色硬币！\n终于！关卡G的红硬币非常的难。等等……我开错游戏了？

column2: This coin looks different... Can I even pay with this...?
You pushed the block in Warping Up the wrong way.\nBut that's harder! Why would you think of doing that!?
column5: 你在上升传送中把砖块推到相反的方向。\n但这样更难啊！你是怎么想到这么做的？

column2: Wait, pushing it to the other side...?
You didn't touch a single warp from the players and won in Warping Up!\nI guess you're getting tired of seeing the same warp over and over all the time.
column5: 你在上升传送中在没有碰到任何多人玩家发射的传送门的情况下获胜！\n我想你反复看到同样的传送门已经累了。

column2: You touched all the blocks in Hunt Trouble.\nNow that's a stylish way of not getting hunted.
column5: 你在狩猎麻烦中碰到了所有的砖块。\n这种躲避狩猎的方式很潇洒。

column2: Being hunted isn't fun unless you touch them all.
column5: 被狩猎并不有趣除非你全部碰到了。

column2: You didn't destroy a single normal block and won in Aiming Tiles!\nYou're a block saver now!
column5: 你在瞄准棋子中在没有破坏任何普通砖块的情况下获胜！\n你现在是个砖块拯救者了！

column2: You went to the opposite corner in A-Maze-Ing.\nWere you that lost?
column5: 你在惊奇迷宫中走到了相反的角落。\n你已经迷路到如此地步了吗？

column2: I'm so lost I'm on the other end!
column5: 我完全找不到北，已经到另一边的尽头了！

column2: You caught the most of or all the small fruits in Catch The Fruits!\nThat level of accuracy must be worth at least 1,000pp
column5: 你在接水果中接到大部分或全部的小水果！\n这准头一定值至少1000分！

column2: It's just like playing osu!\nBut I go small.
column5: 这就像玩osu一样！\n但我要小的。

column2: You caught almost all or all the gordos in Catch The Fruits.\nIs spikes your thing or what?
column5: 你在接水果中接到大部分或全部的刺球。\n你认为刺球是你的财产吗？

column2: Meh fruits isn't the thing for me.
You scored 22 or more in Fitting Squares!\nI bet you can do a T-Spin with that level of precision.
column5: 你在碎片拼图中达到22分或更多！\n我赌你这个准确度随手就能做到T转。

column2: I hope all that Tetris training will pay off.
column5: 我希望那些俄罗斯方块训练会得到回报。

column2: You found all pattern pairs first in Colorful Insanity.\nLosing stuff isn't a problem for you.
column5: 你在色彩衰弱中率先找到所有的成对图案。\n丢东西对你不是问题。

column2: Those finding skills would come in handy when I'm trying to find my keys in my mess.
column5: 这样的搜索技巧能在我从杂物堆中找钥匙的时候帮到大忙。

column2: You touched the piranha plant in Springing Piranha.\nThere's so much dodging at hand and yet you somehow touched the piranha!?
column5: 你在弹射食人花中碰到了食人花。\n有那么多要躲的弹幕但你仍然碰到了食人花！？

column2: Don't worry, that thing is scary so you don't have to worry about touching it.
column5: 不要担心。那个东西很可怕所以你不需要考虑碰它。

column2: You shot before the mark showed up everytime in Western Duel.\nI get that shooting faster is what you're supposed to do, but here you gotta wait for the mark!
column5: 你在西部决斗中每次都在信号出现前开枪。\n我知道你需要更快的开枪，但你需要等待信号！

column2: Waiting for the mark!?\nPfff, I'm faster.
All 4 players died in Western Duel.\nAll of you are either really good or really bad.
column5: 在西部决斗中所有玩家都死了。\n你们所有人要么过于优秀了要么过于糟糕了。

column2: You made the soccer ball land above the net in Soccer Match.\nI'm certainly impressed because getting the ball up there is harder than scoring a goal.
column5: 你在足球比赛中让球落在球网上方。\n我很震惊因为把球踢到那里可比射门难多了。

column2: Great job, now get it back down so we can continue.
column5: 做得好，现在把它拿下来这样我们就能继续了。

column2: You won a Party!\nI want more parties! Bring it on!
column5: 你赢得了一场派对！\n我要更多的派对！放马过来吧！

column2: You lost a Party...\nWell there's always next time I guess.
column5: 你输掉了一场派对……\n嘛，还有下一次的。

column2: Finish a 50 turn Party.\nLook! It's morning outside!
column5: 完成一场50回合的派对。\n看啊！外面天亮了！

column2: You finished a Party with 3 Items.\nOh my, that's such a waste!
column5: 你手持三个道具完成派对。\n我的天，这可真是太浪费了！

column2: Hoarding isn't the best, you know?
column5: 小仓鼠最后一无所有，你知道吗？

column2: You ended a Party with 0 Shines...\nWell that's kinda unfortunate, I mean... that's the whole point, getting Shines.
column5: 你在派对结束的时候没有太阳……\n这真是太不幸了，我想说……这一切的目的都是获得太阳。

column2: Wait... isn't the whole point getting Shines?
column5: 等等……这一切的目的不都是获得太阳？

column2: You won every single minigame in Party Mode!\nI wish I could win all the Minigames as well to gain a bunch of Coins!
column5: 你在派对中赢得所有小游戏！\n我想要赢得所有小游戏，同时赢得很多金币！

column2: You're so much of an expert you won all of them.
column5: 你是如此的优秀，你全都赢下了。

column2: You unlocked all Minigames!\nThe full package is now in your hands!
column5: 你解锁了所有小游戏！\n你现在获得了完整的资料包！

column7: ミニゲームをすべて解放しよう。

column2: You completed all Trials!\nNow you can show off your skills at the Party.
column5: 你完成了全部挑战！\n现在你可以在派对中展现你的技术了。

column2: I can beat all the Trials!
column7: 全てのトライアルをクリアしよう。

column2: You bought everything in the Store!\nThere's just so many things to use, it never ends!
column5: 你买下商店的所有物品！\n有太多可以用的东西了，它永无止境！

column2: I want everything in the Store!
column5: 商店里的东西我全都要了！

column2: You got every single Trophy!!!\nThanks for participating in this Party, hopefully this won't be the last one!
column5: 你获得所有奖杯！！！\n感谢游玩派对，希望这不是最后！
